<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=1858&amp;p=12593#p12593"><![CDATA[
Horst &amp; GauravK:<br /><br />Thanks for all the information. After testing the various combinations, I decided to use the following three:<br />'Disable full row select'<br />'Column headers in all views'<br />Enable icon reordering'<br /><br />They gave me what I was looking for.<br /><br />Horst, your descriptions were a great help in my understanding what each did. There is a small difference from what you wrote. If you select 'Column headers in all views' you are forced to also get 'Enable icon reordering'.<br /><br /><br />Harry<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=64">ac1210</a> — Fri May 02, 2014 10:20 pm</p><hr />
