<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=1858&amp;p=12570#p12570"><![CDATA[
In Folder Options X, you can check any of the first 3 options - all of them force Explorer to use the older ListView control which has narrower spacing. You will have to close and reopen any Explorer windows after you turn on the option in Folder Options X.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=54">Gaurav</a> — Wed Apr 30, 2014 10:30 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
